This Tribecca Home daybed is white, which allows you to easily pair
it with any bedroom color scheme. Add throw pillows to the daybed
to use it as a sofa during the day in a studio or small apartment,
and at night, lie down for a comfortable sleep thanks to the thick
foam padding. The daybed is made of solid hardwood, making it a
durable piece for a frequently used guest room or you child's room.
With vinyl upholstering, the unit is easy to keep clean. The
connected pull-out trundle bed ensures that this daybed adds
